;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';\">0.1V<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  D、通带电压增益为40dB，换算成放大倍数为：100倍，因此放大电路不失真放大时输入电压的范围为：-10\/100~+10\/100，也就是-0.1V~+0.1V。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">只要放大电路的传输特性曲线是线性的，就不会出现失真现象。<\/span>","answer":"wrong","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>传输特性曲线无法反映不同频率信号输入和输出的关系，也就是说，传输特性曲线是线性的，也可能会有线性失真（频率失真）。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">用放大电路放大正弦波信号时，只有可能出现非线性失真，不可能出现频率失真。<\/span>","answer":"correct","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>只有复合频率的信号通过放大电路时才会出现频率失真，正弦信号是单频率信号，所以不会出现频率失真，但会出现由于放大电路非线性关系导致的非线性失真。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">放大电路中的符号“<\/span><strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">^<\/span><\/strong><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">”表示接大地的“地”。<\/span>","answer":"wrong","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>放大电路中的地符号表示电路中的公共参考点，定义为零点位，不一定是大地的地。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">放大电路输出信号增加的能量来自放大电路的工作电源。<\/span>","answer":"correct","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>能量不能无中生有，输出信号中增加的能量来自放大电路的电源，所以放大电路也称为能量控制部件。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">同一个放大电路对不同信号源或带不同负载时，实际的放大能力常常是不同的。<\/span>","answer":"correct","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>由于放大电路的输入电阻通常不是无穷大或零，输出电阻也不会是零或无穷大，所以对于不同的非理想信号源和不同的负载，放大电路的实际增益会有不同。也就是说，在实际信号放大过程中，放大电路的实际增益与输入电阻和输出电阻有关。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">放大电路只有电压增益、电流增益、互阻增益和互导增益四种增益形式。<\/span>","answer":"wrong","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>还有功率增益。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">某放大电路在负载开路时的输出电压为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">4V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，接入<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">3k<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">W<\/span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;font-family:宋体;\">的负载电阻后，输出电压为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">3V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;\">。说明放大电路的输出电阻为<\/span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">        <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';\">1k<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">W<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  C、由输出电阻的计算公式，输出电阻=(负载开路时的电压\/接上负载后的电压-1)*负载电阻=（4\/3-1）*3kΩ=1kΩ."},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">已知某信号源内阻为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">1k<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">W<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，未接放大电路时测得信号源电压为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">10mV<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;\">，接入放大电路后测得放大电路输入端口电压为<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">8mV<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">，说明放大电路的输入电阻为<\/span><span style=\"text-decoration:underline;\"><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">        <\/span><\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">。<\/span>","answer":"<spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'TimesNewRoman','serif';\">4k<\/span><spanstyle=\"font-size:14px;font-family:Symbol;\">W<\/span>","analysis":"<b>解析：<\/b>  C、由输入回路的KVL方程可知：vs*[Ri\/(Ri+Rs)]=vi，因此10*[Ri\/(Ri+1)]=8, <br\/>解方程可得：Ri=4 kΩ。"},{"caption":"<span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">已知某放大电路的最大不失真输出电压范围是－<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">10V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:宋体;\">～＋<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">10V<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family: 宋体;\">，若放大电路的通带电压增益是<\/span><span style=\"font-size:14px;font-family:'Times New Roman','serif';\">40dB<\/span><span styl